{"tid":2507866,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拋棄美元 俄羅斯在與中國貿易中大量使用歐元","createTime":"2021-04-28T09:59:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T10:47:36.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8a3b54d4a832816b2b8edef2eb5f15877d5cb1b7","tid":2507866,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T09:59:20.000Z","msg":"拋棄美元 俄羅斯在與中國貿易中大量使用歐元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%8B%E6%A3%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%9C%A8%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83-164412416.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258B%258B%25E6%25A3%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583-%25E4%25BF%2584%25E7%25BE%2585%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%259C%25A8%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2587%258F%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25AD%2590%25E5%2585%2583-164412416.html&d=APk9rvMsCVL9feuIhYiW0r1zpTq0bGO0w7tnLPpoXkc%3D&h=9c5ce30e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8B%8B%E6%A3%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E5%9C%A8%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E9%87%8F%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83-164412416.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【彭博】-- 俄羅斯總出口中使用美元的比例在去年第四季度首次跌破50%，此前克里姆林宮展開了一場持續多年的運動，以試圖減少該國面對美國資產的脆弱性。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">根據周一公佈的央行數據，減少美元使用的大頭來自俄羅斯與中國的貿易，這部分貿易中超過四分之三目前使用歐元進行。數據顯示，歐元在俄羅斯總出口中使用的比例躍升了10個百分點以上，達到36%。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n多輪制裁以及可能有更多制裁的持續威脅迫使俄羅斯尋找辦法來避免經濟受到美國舉措的干擾。該國央行還大規模減持其國際儲備中的美國國債，同時增持了黃金和歐元。"},{"pid":"dcde4f08c77503542dc05676dad1cae33e245725","tid":2507866,"uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T10:02:24.000Z","msg":"BTC la on9"},{"pid":"091e99980442b6cc66ec82a8d404623a12e26427","tid":2507866,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyT